{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The date and time at which the action was performed.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The name or description of the company.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard This column displays any error messages.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The status of the action. Possible values are:\par
\bullet  \b Created:\b0  Selected data was created successfully\par
\bullet  \b Modified:\b0  Selected data was modified\par
\bullet  \b Removed:\b0  Selected data was removed\par
\pard{\pntext\f0\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\b Error:\b0  Selected data was not created successfully\f0\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The company which the data is copied or updated to.\f0\par
}

}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard Name or description of the source company.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 The unique ID identifying the log.\par
}

}

}
